# LiteMon ğŸ“Š
A lightweight Python function monitoring client decorator & standalone metrics server.

# Overview ğŸš€
LiteMon is a zeroâ€‘config, lightweight monitoring tool that tracks your Python function calls, execution times, and performance metrics in real time.
It comes with a metrics server live dashboard where you can visualize and analyze metrics instantly.
## Features âœ¨

- ğŸ“ˆ Live Dashboard â€“ view real-time metrics at /metrics
- âš¡ Lightweight â€“ no heavy dependencies, minimal config
- ğŸ§© Zero Intrusion â€“ just decorate your functions and monitor them
- ğŸ§¹ Reset Support â€” clear metrics instantly via /reset
- ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» Developer Friendly â€“ perfect for debugging, profiling, and demos


## Installation ğŸ”§

